</p>
<p>Dressing appropriately for air travel means knowing what will keep you comfortable on the plane—and given the cramped seats and various temperature changes on flights, this isn’t always easy.</p>





<h2 class="heading"><strong>What to Wear While Flying: Always Wear These Things on the Plane</strong></h2>




<p>The following items provide plenty of comfort plus a touch of style, making them the best clothes for flying. Be the best dressed in the cabin with our guide to in-flight apparel.</p>



<h2 class="heading"><strong>Layers, Layers, Layers</strong></h2>



<figure class="wp-block-image"><a href="https://www.amazon.com/HappyLuxe-Travel-Blanket-Friendly-Accessories/dp/B01DFT92NI/ref=as_li_ss_tl?imprToken=ZSb.dVt8CSY7lR79zdytsA&amp;slotNum=1&amp;keywords=travel+scarf+blanket&amp;qid=1566488482&amp;s=gateway&amp;sr=8-4&amp;linkCode=sl1&amp;tag=stm07a5-20&amp;linkId=1d6b521e01d0b67ef5c95866456d0dd4&amp;language=en_US" target="_blank" rel="sponsored nofollow"><img loading="lazy" width="1024" height="765" src="https://www.smartertravel.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/wrappp-1024x765.jpg" alt class="wp-image-386435 jetpack-lazy-image" data-lazy-srcset="https://www.smartertravel.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/wrappp-1024x765.jpg 1024w, https://www.smartertravel.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/wrappp-300x224.jpg 300w, https://www.smartertravel.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/wrappp-768x574.jpg 768w, https://www.smartertravel.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/wrappp.jpg 1338w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" data-lazy-src="https://www.smartertravel.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/wrappp-1024x765.jpg?is-pending-load=1" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7"><noscript><img loading="lazy" width="1024" height="765" src="https://www.smartertravel.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/wrappp-1024x765.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-386435" srcset="https://www.smartertravel.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/wrappp-1024x765.jpg 1024w, https://www.smartertravel.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/wrappp-300x224.jpg 300w, https://www.smartertravel.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/wrappp-768x574.jpg 768w, https://www.smartertravel.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/wrappp.jpg 1338w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></noscript></a></figure><p>Air travel is often an assemblage of disparate micro-climates, from the sweat-inducing sunny tarmac to the arctic air-conditioned cabin during flight. Fight that discomfort with plenty of layers like a <a href="https://www.amazon.com/HappyLuxe-Travel-Blanket-Friendly-Accessories/dp/B01DFT92NI/ref=as_li_ss_tl?imprToken=ZSb.dVt8CSY7lR79zdytsA&amp;slotNum=1&amp;keywords=travel+scarf+blanket&amp;qid=1566488482&amp;s=gateway&amp;sr=8-4&amp;linkCode=sl1&amp;tag=stm07a5-20&amp;linkId=1d6b521e01d0b67ef5c95866456d0dd4&amp;language=en_US" target="_blank" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)" rel="sponsored nofollow">washable travel scarf/wrap/blanket hybrid</a> that’s a large enough snuggle underneath when it’s particularly chilly.</p>




