	</script><p>Merino wool is one of the best options for odor and moisture resistance; you can wear it straight off the plane without needing to wash it in between. <a href="https://huckberry.com/store/proof/category/p/56524-72-hour-merino-tee" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Proof’s 72-Hour Merino Tee</a> makes the perfect base layer, and can be worn for 72 hours without acquiring bad smells. For women, consider <a href="https://www.rei.com/product/101388/rei-co-op-merino-midweight-base-layer-top-womens?sku=1013880003&amp;store=80&amp;cm_mmc=PLA_Google%7c21700000001700551_1013880003%7c92700057236781076%7cnone%7c71700000062009822&amp;gclid=Cj0KCQjwk8b7BRCaARIsAARRTL4L2erxKuUwqQ_l1Ov69CtrwfV6Weqd8qC-Wb1XRkHJKobLcYL7KcoaAh1NEALw_wcB&amp;gclsrc=aw.ds" target="_blank" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener">REI Co-op’s Merino Midweight Base Layer Top</a>, which is made from ultra-fine merino wool that’s soft and cozy on cold planes.</p>





<h2 class="heading">Support or Compression Legwear</h2>



<figure class="wp-block-image"><a href="https://www.amazon.com/s/ref=as_li_ss_tl?k=compression+socks&amp;imprToken=ZSb.dVt8CSY7lR79zdytsA&amp;slotNum=17&amp;ref=nb_sb_noss&amp;linkCode=sl2&amp;tag=stm07a5-20&amp;linkId=33dec109f81f5251ed12cb3cba70e2f5&amp;language=en_US" target="_blank" rel="sponsored nofollow"><img loading="lazy" width="1024" height="765" src="https://www.smartertravel.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/comp-1024x765.jpg" alt class="wp-image-386455 jetpack-lazy-image" data-lazy-srcset="https://www.smartertravel.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/comp-1024x765.jpg 1024w, https://www.smartertravel.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/comp-300x224.jpg 300w, https://www.smartertravel.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/comp-768x574.jpg 768w, https://www.smartertravel.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/comp-1536x1147.jpg 1536w, https://www.smartertravel.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/comp.jpg 1754w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" data-lazy-src="https://www.smartertravel.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/comp-1024x765.jpg?is-pending-load=1" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7"><noscript><img loading="lazy" width="1024" height="765" src="https://www.smartertravel.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/comp-1024x765.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-386455" srcset="https://www.smartertravel.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/comp-1024x765.jpg 1024w, https://www.smartertravel.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/comp-300x224.jpg 300w, https://www.smartertravel.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/comp-768x574.jpg 768w, https://www.smartertravel.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/comp-1536x1147.jpg 1536w, https://www.smartertravel.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/comp.jpg 1754w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></noscript></a></figure><p>Many doctors recommend that pregnant women wear support or compression stockings in flight. But compression legwear is also a good choice for those with pre-existing medical conditions, any travelers taking long-haul flights, and anyone who flies often. <a href="https://www.amazon.com/s/ref=as_li_ss_tl?k=compression+socks&amp;imprToken=ZSb.dVt8CSY7lR79zdytsA&amp;slotNum=17&amp;ref=nb_sb_noss&amp;linkCode=sl2&amp;tag=stm07a5-20&amp;linkId=33dec109f81f5251ed12cb3cba70e2f5&amp;language=en_US" target="_blank" aria-label="Compression socks or stockings (opens in a new tab)" rel="sponsored nofollow">Compression socks or stockings</a>, which promote blood circulation, help prevent swelling of the legs, and help guard against deep vein thrombosis (DVT), work by putting pressure on leg muscles and increasing blood flow. These don’t have to look like medical wear either—there are plenty of <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Compression-Socks-Women-Men-Travel-20-25/dp/B07JQXDZLV/ref=as_li_ss_tl?keywords=compression+socks&amp;qid=1566488648&amp;s=gateway&amp;sr=8-9&amp;linkCode=sl1&amp;tag=stm07a5-20&amp;linkId=427a9d1f25d2ece06c3d346b654f1c14&amp;language=en_US" target="_blank" aria-label="stylish compression sock options (opens in a new tab)" rel="sponsored nofollow">stylish compression sock options</a> available.</p>




