<p>For men, <a href="https://publicrec.com/collections/bottoms-pants/products/workday-pant-slim-inseam-32" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Public Rec’s Workday Pants</a> can pass as business casual while hiding plenty of pockets. The pants also have a touch of spandex woven into the fabric to keep you comfortable on long-haul flights.</p>





